nodes.title: Load CLIP Model >
widgets_values:
Get the Clip Model here:

ComfyUI Model Manager > search for "t5" > install 
"t5-v1_1-xxl_encoderonly-fp8_e4m3fn" > click "r" to refresh > select it in the "Load Clip Node.

nodes.title: LOAD UPSCALE MODEL
widgets_values:
I am using https://openmodeldb.info/models/4x-ClearRealityV1. Download and put into ComfyUI\models\upscale_models

You can also use "4x-UltraSharp". You can install that one via the model manager.

Choose your face detector here, MediaPipe doesn't run on GPU and isn't as good at detecting, but is faster on CPU and has Apache 2.0 license.

Insightface can be run on GPU and is better at detecting, but it's model license is NON-COMMERCIAL

nodes.title: LIVE PORTRAIT
widgets_values: If you deactivate the upscale part, you must select 01_VID_GEN here.

nodes.title: FINAL UPSCALE + FACE FIX
widgets_values:
You can Upscale your final output here. 

CTRL+B to bypass the nodes if you don't need them.

nodes.title: PROMPT
widgets_values: A close-up scene of two astronauts in spacesuits on an icy planet, both removing their helmets in a moment of heartbreaking farewell, the female astronaut on the right gently touching the male astronaut's neck, her expression filled with sadness and grief. Both astronauts faces are partially covered with frost, emphasizing the harsh, freezing environment. The icy landscape stretches endlessly in the background, with sharp glaciers. The lighting is soft and diffused, with faint sunlight reflecting off the ice and creating a cold, desolate atmosphere. High quality, ultra-realistic, cinematic style, sharp textures, natural light, photorealistic rendering, emphasizing human emotion in an extreme environment.
